rayon $a^{-\frac{1}{p}}$ lorsque $a\geq 1$. Il vient alors~:
\begin{eqnarray*}
\int_{\mathbb{R}^{n}} f(x)\,dx &=& \int_{0}^{+\infty}
\mu\left(S_{f}(a)\right)\,da = \int_{0}^{1}
\mu\left(\mathcal{B}(0,1) \right)\,da + \int_{1}^{+\infty}
