& = & \frac{\pi^{\frac{n}{2}}}{\Gamma\left(\frac{n}{2}+1\right)} +
\frac{\pi^{\frac{n}{2}}}{\Gamma\left(\frac{n}{2}+1\right)}\int_{1}^{+\infty}
a^{-\frac{n}{p}}\,da.
\end{eqnarray*}
Si $p\geq n$, on obtient $\int_{\mathbb{R}^{n}} f(x)\,dx =+\infty$
